Blanny?

14
00:02:53,060 --> 00:02:55,466
What do you want to say?

15
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:59,240
Didn't you take a vacation?

16
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:03,970
The nurses can take a vacation,
but the patients can not.

17
00:03:04,210 --> 00:03:09,010
Only you went out during the break.

18
00:03:09,010 --> 00:03:10,366
Only me?

19
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:15,610
Right. Natalie and Judy
were in the hospital standing by.

20
00:03:16,790 --> 00:03:19,066
Only me went out.

21
00:03:19,790 --> 00:03:21,290
What can I say?

22
00:03:21,290 --> 00:03:24,073
You are a princess from the Adleys.

23
00:03:24,530 --> 00:03:27,970
It's not true.
I am not related to the Adleys.

24
00:03:27,970 --> 00:03:30,490
I am just a practice nurse.

25
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:33,370
Are you?
Please quit playing around.

26
00:03:33,370 --> 00:03:38,393
The most important thing is
to get used to the new environment.

27
00:03:39,010 --> 00:03:41,710
Yes, you are right.

28
00:03:41,850 --> 00:03:44,246
I will do my best and work harder
from tomorrow.

29
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:48,420
Don't bother my study
if you don't have anything important.

30
00:03:49,450 --> 00:03:51,010
I am sorry.

31
00:03:57,700 --> 00:04:01,100
The hospital are full of patients
because of the accident last night.

32
00:04:01,100 --> 00:04:05,040
The practice nurses from Joseph Hospital
who are still on vacation did a great job.

33
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:07,110
It was an excellent act.

34
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:10,610
The head of our hospital
is very happy about it.

35
00:04:10,610 --> 00:04:14,410
Hope everyone
won't forget the spirit last night,

36
00:04:14,410 --> 00:04:18,606
