outstanding nurse soon.

37
00:04:20,890 --> 00:04:25,750
From now on, you will take turns
to have the night shift.

38
00:04:26,220 --> 00:04:28,950
- Tonight is Blanny.
- Yes.

39
00:04:29,790 --> 00:04:32,590
- Tomorrow is Natalie.
- Yes.

40
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:36,630
