160
00:14:01,930 --> 00:14:03,030
Terry?

161
00:14:03,030 --> 00:14:05,730
I am a fan of Terry.

162
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:10,810
I want to see Terry soon, too.

163
00:14:10,810 --> 00:14:13,040
Is Terry...

164
00:14:13,260 --> 00:14:14,880
He doesn't respect his job.

165
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:18,180
This swollen-headed guy
didn't come to the rehearsal.

166
00:14:18,273 --> 00:14:21,680
Terry is not here.
He must have gone to look for Candy.

167
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:25,420
Won't you leave the flowers to us?

168
00:14:27,990 --> 00:14:31,790
I can't believe
Terry has this kind of friend.

169
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:39,960
Terry?

170
00:14:54,690 --> 00:14:57,413
Knock before you come in,
Miss.Nurse.

171
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:02,526
I am sorry, the harmonica sound...

172
00:15:03,430 --> 00:15:05,660
You heard it?

173
00:15:06,970 --> 00:15:08,690
Did you play it?

174
00:15:08,970 --> 00:15:12,500
Last time I played it,
a nurse with glasses stopped me.

175
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,100
It must be Blanny.

176
00:15:14,906 --> 00:15:16,070
Candy

177
00:15:16,306 --> 00:15:17,440
Blanny

178
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:22,140
How can you put the medicine
in the wrong place?

179
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,670
I am sorry.

180
00:15:24,380 --> 00:15:27,390
You need to be more responsible.

181
00:15:27,390 --> 00:15:28,580
I will pay more attention to that.

182
00:15:30,593 --> 00:15:35,220
How can I do
to let Terry know that I am here?

183
00:15:42,430 --> 00:15:43,566
Wait.

184
00:15:44,093 --> 00:15:45,986
Are you a practice nurse?

185
00:15:47,170 --> 00:15:48,440
Yes.

186
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:50,853
You must know Candy White.

187
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:52,610
We were in the same class.

188
00:15:52,610 --> 00:15:54,910
Anybody came to look for her?

189
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:56,850
No visit allowed on duty.

190
00:15:56,850 --> 00:16:00,320
Candy's shift ends tomorrow morning.

191
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,680
Tomorrow morning?

192
00:16:01,726 --> 00:16:05,246
Did she ask people to
switch the shift with her?

193
00:16:07,860 --> 00:16:11,660
If she asks you,
don't switch it with her.

194
00:16:11,660 --> 00:16:13,130
I won't.

195
00:16:13,930 --> 00:16:15,680
This is the pay.

196
00:16:17,340 --> 00:16:19,040
I can't take it...

197
00:16:19,040 --> 00:16:20,940
Please tell everyone.

198
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:22,300
Stop!

199
00:16:29,410 --> 00:16:31,880
It seems like
he didn't come to the hospital.

200
00:16:31,880 --> 00:16:34,580
Where are you, Terry?

201
00:16:47,100 --> 00:16:49,000
Terry, you are here!

202
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,646
Everyone is looking for you!

203
00:16:51,070 --> 00:16:53,610
I don't want to go to the
performance tonight.

204
00:16:53,610 --> 00:16:55,100
Terry...

205
00:16:56,740 --> 00:16:59,340
The audience are all rich people.

206
00:16:59,340 --> 00:17:02,250
We have no right
to pick our audience.

207
00:17:02,293 --> 00:17:03,350
Is it?

208
00:17:03,350 --> 00:17:07,213
I don't want to serve the celebrities.

209
00:17:07,420 --> 00:17:11,320
But, this is a charity show.

210
00:17:11,320 --> 00:17:13,720
A charity show? Sorry.

211
00:17:14,360 --> 00:17:16,660
Terry, let's go back.

212
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:21,620
Susanna, would the poor
really be helped by this?

213
00:17:22,600 --> 00:17:24,640
This...

214
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:26,740
A real charity show

215
00:17:26,740 --> 00:17:31,026
should be held for those
who can't afford the tickets.

216
00:17:31,810 --> 00:17:33,780
It is right.

217
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:38,040
That harmonica...

218
00:17:38,220 --> 00:17:39,880
Harmonica?

219
00:17:39,880 --> 00:17:45,020
Everytime you are troubled in mind,
it would show up.

220
00:17:55,706 --> 00:17:58,446
From now on, let's replace the
cigarette by the harmonica.

221
00:18:00,970 --> 00:18:03,740
It must be very important to you.

222
00:18:05,180 --> 00:18:06,400
Something replaces the cigarette.

223
00:18:29,930 --> 00:18:32,230
The show starts in thirty minutes.

224
00:18:32,570 --> 00:18:36,840
After tonight, when will be
the next time I see Terry?

225
00:18:41,050 --> 00:18:43,033
I want to fly there.

226
00:18:55,930 --> 00:18:57,260
