227
00:19:04,340 --> 00:19:05,500
What's wrong?

228
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,610
It hurts so much!

229
00:19:08,610 --> 00:19:10,853
Nobody talked to me,
so I started playing the harmonica...

230
00:19:11,210 --> 00:19:13,310
I'll go find the doctor.

231
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:14,710
Thanks.

232
00:19:17,150 --> 00:19:22,453
