236
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:40,710
The reason?

237
00:19:40,833 --> 00:19:45,180
Who do you want to see?
why did you want to switch the shift?

238
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:48,680
Forget it, I already gave up.

239
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:52,240
A guy?

240
00:19:54,890 --> 00:19:59,040
You want to switch the shift
with me for a date?

241
00:20:00,390 --> 00:20:03,120
We live far away.

242
00:20:03,530 --> 00:20:05,890
We don't know
when we will meet again?

243
00:20:07,130 --> 00:20:08,630
So...

244
00:20:08,630 --> 00:20:10,830
You like to cry.

245
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:13,670
Stop it.

246
00:20:13,670 --> 00:20:15,940
Is that person like you?

247
00:20:15,940 --> 00:20:18,000
Drop it, Natalie.

248
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:20,880
I'll switch it with you.

249
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:24,580
Natalie.

250
00:20:25,020 --> 00:20:28,253
Blanny is in the library, it's ok.

251
00:20:29,420 --> 00:20:31,306
Are you sure, natalie?

252
00:20:32,020 --> 00:20:36,830
I was always afraid to
get into trouble since I was a child.

253
00:20:36,830 --> 00:20:38,746
And now I am Blanny's follower.

254
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:41,130
Then why would you...

255
00:20:41,130 --> 00:20:42,960
Blanny won't blame me.

256
00:20:43,100 --> 00:20:44,470
Natalie.

257
00:20:44,470 --> 00:20:47,706
Honestly, I don't really like you.

258
00:20:50,340 --> 00:20:53,710
But, I met someone
who I dislike more.

259
00:20:54,210 --> 00:20:57,410
Who tries to win people's hearts
by money.

260
00:20:58,620 --> 00:21:00,120
Was it...

261
00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:01,990
Give her back the money!

262
00:21:01,990 --> 00:21:05,113
She is about the same age with us.
You know who she is, right?

263
00:21:06,590 --> 00:21:08,073
Elisa?

264
00:21:09,193 --> 00:21:11,486
Go change your clothes.

265
00:21:12,460 --> 00:21:14,520
Thank you, Natalie!

266
00:21:14,800 --> 00:21:16,730
Don't let Blanny find out
about this.

267
00:21:28,180 --> 00:21:29,680
Candy is so slow.

268
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,880
The show starts in five minutes.

269
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:33,393
Annie, she is not here yet?

270
00:21:35,650 --> 00:21:37,140
Not yet.

271
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:45,726
Sorry, please hurry.

272
00:21:50,330 --> 00:21:53,270
I am going to see Terry soon.

273
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:56,010
Terry, I am coming!

274
00:21:56,010 --> 00:21:58,980
We will be able to see each other
in five minutes.

275
00:22:02,210 --> 00:22:06,010
